nomenclaturalStatus: nom. inval.    On p. 66, the genus name Acrocomia is published; on p. 67, Cocos aculeata Jacq. is assigned to Acrocomia, but the new combination 'A. aculeata' is not made

nom. inval. nom. nud.    The protologue shows the name as “Acrocomia aculeata” as a nom. nud and without an authorship; even an indirect reference to the intended basionym Cocos aculeata Jacq. is lacking.
